  "Description": {
    "English": "A critical freighter subsystem, vital for maintaining a habitable and safe environment for all on-board organic lifeforms.<br><br>Capable of generated a limited <span class=\"name name-stellar\">breathable atmosphere</span> even when damaged or unpowered, but only for a short period of time.",
